  m_Name: Item_Card_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9468c17b4d71ffb4c91a88932a469897, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 126418915328
    m_Localized: POWER Card
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126465052672
    m_Localized: POWER of all units is increased by 5% for all units.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126465052673
    m_Localized: AttackSpeed Card
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126465052674
    m_Localized: AttackSpeed  increases by 4% for all units.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246976
    m_Localized: HP Card
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246977
    m_Localized: HP increases by 30 for all units.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246978
    m_Localized: Cooltime Reduction Card
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246979
    m_Localized: The cooltime of passive and active patterns of all units is reduced
      by 5%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246980
    m_Localized: Onemanshow
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246981
    m_Localized: If there is only one unit, that unit's POWER increases by 100%,
      attack speed increases by 40%, and HP decreases by 50%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246982
    m_Localized: Titanification
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246983
    m_Localized: All units' HP increases by 20%. The size of the units increases
      by 20%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246984
    m_Localized: Sticky Trap
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246985
    m_Localized: Sticky traps are placed in the front two vertical lines. The sticky
      traps slow down monsters by 60%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246986
    m_Localized: Hold the Line!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246987
    m_Localized: All units' POWER increases by 70%, HP by 20%, and attack speed by
      30%, but switching cannot be used in any round except for the breakStage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246988
    m_Localized: Stretching
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246989
    m_Localized: The range of Range-Attacker units increases by 2 tiles, and their
      attack speed increases by 20%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246990
    m_Localized: Best Partner
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246991
    m_Localized: Unit 1 and Unit 2 each create a 3x3 range. If these ranges overlap,
      both units' POWER increases by 30%, attack speed by 30%, and monsters within
      the range are slowed by 50%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246992
    m_Localized: Hold On!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246993
    m_Localized: If there is an Range-Attacker unit on the field, all units gain
      an HP regeneration rate of +6 HP per second.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246994
    m_Localized: Encore
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246995
    m_Localized: If there is a supporter unit on the field, all units gain a resurrection
      ability. Resurrected units receive a 50% attack speed buff for 5 seconds (cooldown
      70 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246996
    m_Localized: Juice Party
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246997
    m_Localized: 'All units are granted the effect: "When casting a basic pattern,
      there is a 30% chance to throw a poison vial at a random tile." The poison
      vial deals 90 damage to the tile''s area.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246998
    m_Localized: Ammo Supply
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469246999
    m_Localized: 'Projectile units gain the effect: "When casting a basic pattern,
      they fire 2 magic bullets that deal damage proportional to their POWER."'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469247000
    m_Localized: Overclock
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469247001
    m_Localized: Each time an active pattern is used, all units shoot a "whirlwind
      projectile" that deals 50 damage. Additionally, the cooldown of each active
      pattern is reduced by 1% whenever it is used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469247002
    m_Localized: Heavy Attack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 126469247003
    m_Localized: All units' POWER increase by 50%, but their attack speed decreases
      by 20%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1785497846779904
    m_Localized: You will not receive any effect even if you select this. as the
      condition is not met.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 36397880783114240
    m_Localized: 'Select the desired ability card. You can choose a total of 2 times:
      once at Boss Stage 1 and once at Boss Stage 5.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
